title: Demon in Mount Hua
description: Demon in Mount Hua MANHWAThe Murim’s public enemy, the Slaughterer Demon Monarch, Yeom Se-Ak! It’s been a hundred years since he was trapped in Mount Hua after being captured by the Sword God, Han Ho. He waited all these years for his chance to seek revenge… The long period of time caused this incident to be forgotten by the world, and eventually, even the Yeom Se-Ak was forgotten. But. “Sir, what is your name…?” A coincidental meeting, and the name of an archenemy that he said unwittingly, “H-Han Ho.” At the end of a vain journey, an unexpected path branches out. The ultimate demon that’s in Mount Hua, Yeom Se-Ak’s choice! Demon in Mount Hwa 魔in華山 마IN화산 마인화산
